### Development Setup

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/LeaveMyYard/Tresto.git
cd Tresto

# Install dependencies with uv
uv sync --dev

# Install pre-commit hooks
pre-commit install

# Run tests
pytest

# Run linting
ruff check .
mypy .
```

